{"tid":2514744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Bomba如果無走錯路，今日會唔會係五台聯播，而且係五台之首？","createTime":"2021-05-03T12:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T08:39:24.000Z","uid":205394,"like":42,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b7122ca14be6f21a876fd791d9f4059df75f385f","tid":2514744,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"答案係<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">唔會呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為你地係<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\">死藍絲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過認真討論<br />\n假設佢地係黃而且無自我澎漲，走錯路<br />\n其實佢當年拍既片的確有一定水準<br />\n就用而家最能代表香港YouTube界既四台同佢作個比較<br />\n<br />\n先比較認真拍既片，即係微電影類<br />\n佢地運鏡同色調既應用的確同當年同期既youtuber比較都尤為出眾<br />\n四台派出佢地都公認出產高質片既熊仔頭既微電影去同bomba挑機<br />\n熊仔頭當年既認真系列同bomba既認真系列其實睇得出個格局同鏡頭既表達力都輸bomba唔少<br />\n就算係四年後既今日既熊仔頭同四年前全盛期bomba比較<br />\n拍攝技巧都重係有d距離<br />\n當然，熊仔頭既微電影勝在劇本同演員本身既魅力<br />\nBomba既劇本就無佢地咁有趣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但bomba重兼顧到低成本既片<br />\n會有高成本既認真片之外都會一直出低成本既搞笑片<br />\n產量方面屌打單方面集中係高成本片既熊仔頭<br />\n當然，bomba未去到啱channel，小薯茄咁出咁多咁密<br />\n但佢地出片頻率都絕唔差<br />\n<br />\n以成員來講<br />\nBomba既成員，<br />\n首席女幕前kikko 又唔算好差，演技都合格既<br />\n但真係除左kikko 就無第二個打得既女幕前囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以女幕前我認為四台都屌打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反，男幕前就有felix 同爆江<br />\n佢地雖然唔算靚仔，但絕對係有住好強既觀眾緣<br />\n尤其爆江，真係自帶搞笑效果，佢果種反應同表達真係有佢獨特性<br />\n男幕前有可以同四台唔錯既競爭力<br />\n<br />\n大家又有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n利申，fox真係好撚黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35354d28966b44a816f8f7e80d390be58afc4134","tid":2514744,"uid":79793,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:37:50.000Z","msg":"其實應該會<br />\n最後會變香港微辣<br />\n變成一間大公司,出咩廢片都有人睇"},{"pid":"0a3554df26233e157c756dd6df18c3a7a2711de2","tid":2514744,"uid":345520,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:38:41.000Z","msg":"Fox 一個累全家"},{"pid":"dd393a9ade81567b117fe0becb82507335903fe6","tid":2514744,"uid":2959,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾徵費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740c08df95ece768c1a899acf1147246a3815781","tid":2514744,"uid":205394,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"35354d28966b44a816f8f7e80d390be58afc4134","tid":2514744,"uid":79793,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:37:50.000Z","msg":"其實應該會<br />\n最後會變香港微辣<br />\n變成一間大公司,出咩廢片都有人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"咁又唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起碼重有清泉熊仔頭<br />\n熊仔頭而家都係逆住YouTube主流經營方式去經營YouTube<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油熊人仔頭"},{"pid":"0a57eeead8742b66870bdf84077ffc07409a0b8f","tid":2514744,"uid":8219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:47:59.000Z","msg":"唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752ca3d65a445065e5af9d875020bed820891fdf","tid":2514744,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a0dd8a1d51e1689f5cfde3e562c695cf64c21d","tid":2514744,"uid":367270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd393a9ade81567b117fe0becb8250733